      <guid>https://bbhtt.space/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I’m Nobody! Who are you? Are you – Nobody – too? Then there’s a pair of us!&lt;/em&gt; ~ Emily Dickinson&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello and welcome to my little corner of the internet!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You might know me by my online alias, &lt;em&gt;bbhtt&lt;/em&gt;. I live in India and I am
currently pursuing a Ph.D. in Mathematics. I teach Mathematics for work
and occasionally contribute to &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Free_and_open-source_software&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;FOSS projects&lt;/a&gt;
during my free time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I enjoy watching &lt;a href=&#34;https://letterboxd.com/bbhtt/films/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;movies&lt;/a&gt;,
TV shows, and &lt;a href=&#34;https://anidb.net/user/983003&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;anime&lt;/a&gt;. I try to read books
every now and then but I love listening to &lt;a href=&#34;https://open.spotify.com/user/m18qz71984e1gjbkfbd36zwmi&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;music&lt;/a&gt;
and spending too much time on YouTube! Occasionally, I play games on &lt;a href=&#34;https://steamcommunity.com/id/bbhtt/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Steam&lt;/a&gt;
and dive into casual online chess, although I never studied it
seriously.&lt;/p&gt;
